were reached with the participation of the Organization of the Islamic Conference (OIC), and its 
reports clarify the issues of contention.  <i>See</i> &#8220;Report of the Secretary-General on the Question of 
Muslims in Southern Philippines&#8221; (OIC/33-ICFM/2005/MM/SG/REP.2) (issued June 2006). 
